<el-container>
    <el-main style="margin: auto;width:100%">
        <el-table
                :data="tableData"
                style="width: 100%"
                :default-sort = "{prop: 'date', order: 'descending'}"
        >
            <el-table-column
                    prop="date"
                    label="日期"
                    sortable
                    width="180">
            </el-table-column>
            <el-table-column
                    prop="name"
                    label="姓名"
                    sortable
                    width="180">
            </el-table-column>
            <el-table-column
                    prop="address"
                    label="地址"
                    :formatter="formatter">
            </el-table-column>
        </el-table>
    </el-main>
    <el-footer style="margin: auto">
        <el-container>
            <el-rate style="width:100%;"
                     v-model="value2"
                     :colors="colors">
            </el-rate>
        </el-container>
    </el-footer>
</el-container>
